{"tid":1429336,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲貿易部長:  美國向中國徵關稅, 為此對美國感到失望","createTime":"2019-08-07T13:07:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T13:35:10.000Z","uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"846f74a450f189ac2068f80fec3bf9282269ee7d","tid":1429336,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:07:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2874479\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2874479&d=12Rr7FHSceVDny91Y6RlLJdwtLMCc893KahbJtTxKsc%3D&h=5b244004\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2874479&h=408953c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2874479</a><br />\n<br />\n川普對中國徵稅 澳洲部長：可能違反WTO規定<br />\n2019-08-05 14:36<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美中貿易戰持續延燒，美國總統川普宣布自9月起將對剩餘3000億美元的中國商品加徵10％關稅，全球經濟再添風險。對此，澳大利亞貿易部長伯明翰（Simon Birmingham）日前接受當地媒體採訪時表示，對川普的做法感到失望，並認為可能違反世界貿易組織（WTO）的相關規定。<br />\n<br />\n根據德國之聲報導，伯明翰對於川普政府宣布要對中國商品加徵關稅一事提出看法，他認為雖然尚未生效，「但若是最終達成，有可能會違反WTO的規則」；據報導，伯明翰也提及，這些單方面的關稅行動，不是我們所歡迎的，雖然可能違反WTO規則，但仍屬於獨立程序的一部分。<br />\n<br />\n據該報導指出，川普在推特發文宣稱關稅措施讓美國財政部從中國獲得數十億美元收入，但實際上，這些關稅其實是由美國進口商的中間商支付，且在大多數情況下，最終都是由美國消費者支付。"},{"pid":"eb5e7749f612dca1f75e480e59ed9ad269664d9c","tid":1429336,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:08:43.000Z","msg":"澳洲總理極為欽佩Donald Trump, 但都攪成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6809/3821667\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6809%2F3821667&d=12Rr7FHSceVDny91Y6RlLJdwtLMCc893KahbJtTxKsc%3D&h=54de2592\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6809/3821667</a><br />\n<br />\n澳洲總理莫里森連任 顯示川普「國家主義之春」擴大<br />\n2019-05-19 13:51<br />\n<br />\n華盛頓時報分析，澳洲保守派總理莫里森爆冷保住江山，顯示由美國總統川普掀起的「國家主義之春」（the Nationalist Spring）仍然很活躍，且聲勢日益擴大。<br />\n<br />\n莫里森是一位極為欽佩川普的福音派基督徒，川普毫不掩飾他領導的政府，要將美國利益放在第一位。莫里森也如是，他在勝利演說中聲言，「澳洲人依靠政府將他們放在第一位，這正是我們要做的。」<br />\n<br />\n分析指出，推動莫里森出乎意料取得勝利的力量，是「澳洲第一」的選民心態，被廣泛稱為「民粹主義者」。美國、英國、義大利、匈牙利、巴西及其他地區也有類似的選民，在涉及墮胎、宗教、稅收、經濟、移民等問題上愈趨保守。"},{"pid":"341f541a0b5f86810c221aece958a39b27f900cb","tid":1429336,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:10:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff8a5370664d5c38b095d48dda4e7003f156ab9f","tid":1429336,"uid":197989,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:19:57.000Z","msg":"人地侵侵已經去到唔承認WTO嘅行為<br />\n聲明怪責WTO比世界第二強國做&quot;發展中國家&quot;<br />\n依家話美國違反範定?<br />\n人地真係好驚丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a74bf83c819a96cd7c8e2dad024f8d318884b28","tid":1429336,"uid":65790,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:26:26.000Z","msg":"含撚政府-澳洲"},{"pid":"35de04f885e4fe03de67859b01fffb77698629e1","tid":1429336,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:28:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcd334726d5a77796b8d91157f90aafabd715349","tid":1429336,"uid":54125,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:31:26.000Z","msg":"澳洲都變半個中國啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aececb18a498adf83b6e9f45d9999347aadc8ac","tid":1429336,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:32:29.000Z","msg":"中國豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d1b5d914d4a92c54cb5d3dde2ce245194148d55","tid":1429336,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:33:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16efb1d13a5126f3c65da4733565cf655ed1ffd4","tid":1429336,"uid":224066,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:35:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tBBjvN2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtBBjvN2.jpg&h=3f6032ff&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}